# Testing Conventions

## Test Suites
```
Unit/     → Services, helpers, value objects — no DB, no HTTP
Feature/  → HTTP requests, DB interactions — uses RefreshDatabase
Tenant/   → Tenant-scoped Feature tests — auto-creates Company + User
```

## TenantTestCase Base Class
```php
// All tenant feature tests extend this
abstract class TenantTestCase extends TestCase
{
    use RefreshDatabase;

    protected Company $company;
    protected User $admin;

    protected function setUp(): void
    {
        parent::setUp();

        $this->company = Company::factory()->create();
        $this->admin   = User::factory()
            ->for($this->company)
            ->withRole('company_admin')
            ->create();

        // Simulate subdomain resolution
        app()->instance('currentCompany', $this->company);
    }

    protected function actingAsAdmin(): static
    {
        return $this->actingAs($this->admin);
    }

    protected function actingAsMember(): static
    {
        $member = User::factory()->for($this->company)->withRole('team_member')->create();
        return $this->actingAs($member);
    }
}
```

## Test Structure — Given / When / Then
```php
/** @test */
public function company_admin_can_create_invoice(): void
{
    // Given
    $client = Client::factory()->for($this->company)->create();

    // When
    $response = $this->actingAsAdmin()
        ->postJson('/api/v1/invoices', [
            'client_id' => $client->id,
            'due_date'  => now()->addDays(30)->toDateString(),
            'items'     => [
                ['description' => 'Design work', 'quantity' => 1, 'unit_price' => 150000]
            ],
        ]);

    // Then
    $response->assertCreated();
    $response->assertJsonPath('data.status', 'draft');
    $this->assertDatabaseHas('invoices', [
        'company_id' => $this->company->id,
        'client_id'  => $client->id,
        'status'     => 'draft',
    ]);
}
```

## What to Test Per Feature
```
✓ Happy path (success case)
✓ Unauthorized access (403)
✓ Wrong tenant cannot access another tenant's resource (403/404)
✓ Validation errors (422)
✓ Plan limit exceeded (402/403)
✓ Not found (404)
✓ Edge cases specific to the feature
```

## Coverage Targets
```
Domain/     → 85% minimum
Services/   → 85% minimum
Controllers → 70% minimum (covered via Feature tests)
Models      → relationships + scopes tested
```

## Commands
```bash
php artisan test --testsuite=Unit     # fast, no DB
php artisan test --testsuite=Feature  # full HTTP
php artisan test --testsuite=Tenant   # tenant-scoped
php artisan test --coverage --min=80  # enforce coverage
```
